# GitHub Linguist counts bytes per language. The executed notebook embeds
# base64 PNG graphs + cell outputs, so it is large and would otherwise dominate
# the repo's language bar. Mark notebooks as documentation so the language
# stats reflect the actual source (Python + TypeScript).
*.ipynb linguist-documentation

# Keep generated/exported web data out of the language stats too.
web/public/data/*.json linguist-generated
